state.title: AccessDenied
state.tooltip: Whenever one of your agents, be it a rake or gentleman, selects a viable target this will appear.||You will be presented with a selection of actions to perform depending on your agent and your target.||Move your cursor over the options for more details.

uiEntry.title: assassinate
uiEntry.tooltip: You have a chance to use your assassination skills here.||Clicking on this will open up the Assassination panel.||The opportunity to dispose of a potential threat or competition can be risky.||The Assassination panel will provide you with the percentage chance of success.

uiEntry.title: embed
uiEntry.tooltip: Your spies have the ability to infiltrate and spy on armies and settlements.|| Through their watchful eyes you can gather information about other nations that may otherwise be hidden from you.|| To see the information, simply left-click on the infiltrated army or city.|| Discovery is always a risk, and even if your spy evades death or capture your nation will be looked upon with suspicion from then on.|| If the chance of success is low you may want to think twice before attempting an infiltration.

uiEntry.title: sabotage
uiEntry.tooltip: You have been given the option of sabotage - a chance to wreak some havoc!||Clicking on this will open up your Sabotage panel.||The Sabotage panel will help you decide whether or not this is the course of action you wish to pursue.

uiEntry.title: research
uiEntry.tooltip: This agent is a learned man, and can use his education to the advancement of your nation.||Clicking on this button will move your agent into the selected school, college or university and bring up the Research and Technology panel.||A gentlemen in a college or university will help speed up any research undertaken there.||See the Research and Technology panel for more details.

uiEntry.title: steal_research
uiEntry.tooltip: Fate has provided you with the opportunity to steal research - time to use those light fingers of yours!|| Clicking on this button brings up the Research and Technology panel where potential swag can be browsed.|| Keep in-mind that knowledge may come at a price - stealing the work of another may end with the capture of your agent and the exposure of your nation's dirty dealing!

uiEntry.title: duel
uiEntry.tooltip: Duelling is the proper way to resolve disagreements and disputes.||This button will open up the Duel panel which will give you more tips about duelling and its use.

uiEntry.title: visit
uiEntry.tooltip: Select this if you wish to visit without performing a specific action.||Your agent can always perform an action on the next turn.
